Modern Hanukkah Star of David Snowman Wreath Holiday Card if you are looking for it, we recommend it Modern Hanukkah Star of David Snowman Wreath Holiday Card There are many featuresCelebrate the Jewish holidays with this beautiful and unique greeting card. What a beautiful card to bless your friends and family during the Festival of Lights. This modern design features a happy snowman wearing a blue velvet top hat with a Star of David on the brim, earmuffs, mittens, and a blue striped scarf. The wreath contains beautiful snowflakes, poinsettias, icicles, and the Star of David in various designs. The plaque in the middle includes the inspirational message: "Scatter kindness like snowflakes." The text reads "Happy Hanukkah." The back of the card reads "Hanukkah Sameach! Enjoy this festival to the fullest!" along with a beautiful blue snowy border. All text may be deleted or edited for personalization at no additional charge. Choose matte or semi-gloss finish. Wreath photographed at the Festival of Trees, Orlando Museum of Art, by Glenda Motsavage, travel writer and author. Price:$1.99
